description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Brady Quinn about Kenny Pickett's outlook in the NFL. Current 3-point record holder Ray Allen tells us that he plans to be in attendance when Steph Curry breaks his record. And Actor Zachary Levi finds out that he may be related to DP.
